DOC.brief_summary: This study will evaluate the efficacy of Ozurdex® as prescribed in clinical practice in France for the treatment of Diabetic Macular Edema (DME).
DOC.brief_title: Efficacy of Ozurdex® in the Treatment of Diabetic Macular Edema (DME)
DOC.criteria: Patient with Diabetic Macular Edema (DME) treated with Ozurdex® in clinical practice. Patient not residing in metropolitan France.
